    "The upward trend from 2018 onwards corresponds with the period following the formal introduction of STEM integration policies in China around 2017, which likely spurred increased academic activity and publication output in subsequent years (Fig. 3).",
    "The following were the criteria used to choose the case studies:",
    "(1) The studies adhered to the criteria for high-quality TPD (Borko et al. 2010 (Borko et al., 2011;; Stein et al. 2009) (Borko et al. 2010 (Borko et al., 2011;; Stein et al. 2009) criteria for high-quality TPD in at least three ways.",
    "After looking at what other researchers had suggested as characteristics of good TPDs, Borko et al. (2010) discovered that most people agreed on the critical features of successful TPD programs (Appendix II).",
    "(2) These traits are in line with what Opfer and Pedder (2011), Postholm (2012), and Avalos (2011) say is essential in highquality TPD programs."
  ]
}